product_name: Nite Ize Stainless-Steel S-Biner Size 1 - Package of 2
long_description: The Nite Ize Stainless-Steel S-Biner Size 1 is a unique double-clip carabiner that offers a great way to manage your keys or other items. Praising the S-Biner, Backpacker April '08 declared, ''Don't ask yourself if you need this useful little widget. The question is: How many?''. Dual hook design with opposing gates allow you to easily link 2 items together. Rugged stainless steel and secure gate closure. The Nite Ize Stainless-Steel S-Biner Size 1 is rated to hold up to 5 lbs.
